{"type":"message","id":"9227d298","parentId":"4fda6791","timestamp":"2026-03-27T06:12:33.715Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-27 14:12:32 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb [msg:om_x100b5355b2250ca4c4c6b210513db45]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5355b2250ca4c4c6b210513db45\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-03-27 14:12 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\"\n}\n```\n\n你吧那个选品agent先建立上， 为我们看那怎么调整。"}],"timestamp":1774591953589}}
{"type":"message","id":"5dabd557","parentId":"9227d298","timestamp":"2026-03-27T06:12:52.615Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"User says: \"你吧那个选品agent先建立上， 为我们看那怎么调整。\" Chinese: they want to set up a product selection agent (选品agent) first, and then see how to adjust it. Probably they want to create a new agent or subagent? According to SOUL, we have role as chief assistant, can spawn subagents. There's a \"dev\" agent for technical tasks. Possibly they want to create an agent for product selection. We need to ask clarification: what exactly is needed? Maybe they want a subagent that handles product selection? We could spawn a subagent session with a task description. According to guidelines, we should ask the user for specifics? The request: \"你吧那个选品agent先建立上， 为我们看那怎么调整。\" Means \"you first set up that product selection agent, and then see how to adjust it for us.\" They want to set up an agent. We could ask details: what functions should it have, what tasks? Or we could assume they want a generic agent that helps with product selection. Might need to create a sub-agent via sessions_spawn with appropriate task. Use model default.\n\nWe should ask for clarification about the desired capabilities. Probably it's better to ask what they expect the agent to do. So respond asking for requirements.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]]  \n好的，我先准备把选品 Agent 搭建好。为了确保它能满足你的需求，请你帮我确认以下几点：\n\n1. **核心功能**：  \n   - 需要它帮助筛选、评估或推荐哪些类型的商品？（比如电商平台、品类、目标用户等）  \n   - 是否需要它连接到飞书的多维表格、任务或日历等工具来记录和跟进？\n\n2. **数据来源**：  \n   - 选品时会使用哪些数据？（内部数据库、公开的商品 API、文档、表格等）  \n   - 如果有已有的多维表格或文档，请提供对应的 **app_token / table_id / 文档链接**，方便我让 Agent 直接读取。\n\n3. **交互方式**：  \n   - 你希望通过飞书聊天直接与 Agent 对话，还是通过任务/日程的形式交付结果？  \n   - 是否需要自动创建任务或日程提醒（比如每周一次推荐）？\n\n4. **输出格式**：  \n   - 需要返回的内容是表格、列表、富文本卡片，还是直接生成飞书文档？  \n\n提供这些信息后，我就可以用 `sessions_spawn` 为你创建一个专属的选品 Agent （子会话），并把它配置好，随后再一起看看如何进一步调整。谢谢！"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/auto","usage":{"input":25852,"output":918,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":26770,"cost":{"input":-25852,"output":-918,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":-26770}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774591953721,"responseId":"gen-1774591957-nEGaQuKlgw9G6R5ifX9h"}}
{"type":"message","id":"4b12dfad","parentId":"5dabd557","timestamp":"2026-03-27T06:16:22.677Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-27 14:16:21 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb [msg:om_x100b53564583a878b4cc187e5bc0e31, post]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b53564583a878b4cc187e5bc0e31\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-03-27 14:16 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\"\n}\n```\n\n**关于 TikTok 选品 Agent 的详细定义补充：**\n**1. 核心功能与筛选逻辑：**\n- **平台：** 专注 TikTok (Web版)。\n- **品类：** 主要是 [填入你关注的品类，如：家居、智能小家电、快时尚]。\n- **筛选标准：** 过去 24 小时内播放量突破 100k、且评论区有高频“Where to buy”或“Link please”关键词的视频。\n- **评估逻辑：** 识别视频中的商品 -> 调用 LLM 进行爆款潜力打分（1-100）-> 预估毛利分析。\n**2. 数据来源与工具：**\n- **实时抓取：** 使用 OpenClaw 的 browser 工具访问 [tiktok.com](tiktok.com) 搜索关键词或爬取 Trending 页面。\n- **参考资料：** 结合 [如果有的话，可以填入你的历史选品 Excel 或 竞争对手链接]。\n**3. 交互方式与集成：**\n- **入口：** 我希望通过**飞书聊天窗口**直接发送指令（如：“开始今日家居类目选品”）。\n- **自动化：** 配置一个 cron 任务，每天 [北京时间 10:00] 自动运行一次并汇总。\n**4. 输出格式与落地：**\n- **即时通知：** 发现潜力分 > 85 的商品时，立即发送**飞书富文本消息卡片**，包含：商品名、视频链接、推荐理由。\n- **归档记录：** 所有筛选出的商品需自动同步到**飞书多维表格 (Bitable)**。\n  - *App Token:* [请填入你的 Bitable App Token，或先填 \"PLACEHOLDER\"]\n  - *Table ID:* [请填入 Table ID，或先填 \"PLACEHOLDER\"]\n**5. 开发要求：**\n- 请先为我生成一个名为 tiktok_scout 的 **Skill**，用于处理 TikTok 网页爬取和数据清洗（使用浏览器自动化）。\n- 然后利用 sessions_spawn 创建这个专属 Agent，并将该 Skill 挂载给它。"}],"timestamp":1774592182674}}
