{"type":"message","id":"d6b8138a","parentId":"a4a932b6","timestamp":"2026-03-27T06:17:37.648Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"We have spawned a subagent for tiktok_scout. Need to wait for its completion events. The system expects us to eventually reply with results after subagent finishes. We should perhaps note that we have set up the skill file and cron, and spawned the agent. The subagent will run with task \"tiktok_scout\". We need to wait for its output. According to instructions, we should not poll, just wait for its messages. So we need to respond to user after subagent finishes. For now we can acknowledge that the agent is being set up. Possibly need to tell user that the skill and agent are ready, and the cron job is set. Provide details.\n\nWe should not send another tool call now. The user asked to generate skill and spawn agent. We have done that. So reply summarizing.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]]  \n已完成以下操作：\n\n1. **创建了 `tiktok_scout` Skill**（位于 `~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/tiktok_scout/SKILL.md`），该技能使用 `agent-browser` 实现 TikTok 网页抓取、数据过滤、LLM 打分、毛利预估，并将结果同步到 Feishu 多维表格以及通过富文本卡片即时通知。\n\n2. **添加了每日定时任务**  \n   - 名称：`TikTok Daily Scout`  \n   - 时间：每天 **北京时间 10:00**（Cron 表达式 `0 2 * * *`，对应 UTC 02:00）  \n   - 触发方式：在子会话中运行 `tiktok_scout`，完成后自动在本会话中以公告形式发送结果。\n\n3. **启动了专属的选品 Agent**（子会话 `agent:main:subagent:fca6ce70-f385-4ee4-bc9d-a82f0e93136f`），它会立即执行一次 TikTok 选品流程，并在完成后把发现的高潜力商品（评分 > 85）返回给你。\n\n稍后你会收到子 Agent 的执行结果——包括符合条件的商品名单、视频链接、评分、预计毛利以及对应的 Bitable 记录链接。如果还有其他自定义需求（如更改品类、阈值或通知方式），随时告诉我！"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/auto","usage":{"input":31989,"output":697,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32686,"cost":{"input":-31989,"output":-697,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":-32686}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774592246300,"responseId":"gen-1774592247-l4RLgG8Clkpf30FK5ZH7"}}
