{"type":"message","id":"62b75ecc","parentId":"c3b3414e","timestamp":"2026-03-27T06:31:23.412Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-27 14:31:21 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb [msg:om_x100b53560d45a8a0c1485b1b6b3a092]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b53560d45a8a0c1485b1b6b3a092\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-03-27 14:31 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\"\n}\n```\n\n可以了"}],"timestamp":1774593083407}}
{"type":"message","id":"2a9e68fd","parentId":"62b75ecc","timestamp":"2026-03-27T06:31:41.191Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"We need to create a new Skill tts_hair_scout (or tts_scout?). The user wants tts_hair_scout independent subagent. They need SKILL.md and index.ts source code. We should create a folder under workspace/skills/tts_hair_scout with SKILL.md and index.ts. The SKILL.md should follow similar pattern as earlier but with description. Then create index.ts (or js) for the skill logic. We need to output index.ts content to user after creation.\n\nWe must ensure we read skill template? There's a skill-creator skill but not needed. We'll create the files.\n\nFirst, create SKILL.md for tts_hair_scout. Then create index.ts. Provide code that uses agent-browser to fetch TikTok, parse, filter, calculate ROI, use LLM.\n\nSimplify: index.ts will be a TypeScript script referenced by OpenClaw skill runtime. The skill spec says we can have scripts like index.ts used by skill. So create a basic skeleton that defines async function main(params). We'll include placeholders.\n\nLet's create folder.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_554f2ea46275499182","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"---\nname: tts_hair_scout\ndescription: TikTok (Web) scouting for hair accessories (发饰) with custom ROI and LLM scoring.\nread_when:\n  - \"需要运行 TTS 选品\"\nmetadata:\n  requires:\n    bins: [\"agent-browser\"]\nallowed-tools:\n  - Bash(agent-browser:*)\n---\n\n# TTS Hair Scouting Skill\n\nThis skill runs in an **isolated sub‑agent** and performs the following steps:\n1. Launches `agent-browser` to open TikTok Trending / search page for the specified hair‑accessory keywords.\n2. Snapshots the page, extracts video links, view counts and comment excerpts.\n3. Filters videos with **last 24 h views ≥ 100 k** and comments containing any of the purchase‑intent keywords.\n4. Calls the LLM (via the main agent) with a prompt to score the product’s visual impact & social virality (0‑100).\n5. Computes a simple ROI using the provided formula.\n6. If **score > 85**, sends a Feishu rich‑card notification and writes a record into the target Bitable table.\n\n## Parameters (passed from the parent agent)\n```json\n{\n  \"category\": \"Hair Accessories\",\n  \"subcategories\": [\"Hair Clips/Headbands\", \"Hairpins/Hair Ties\"],\n  \"view_threshold\": 100000,\n  \"keywords\": [\"where to buy\", \"link please\", \"is it on shop\", \"how much\", \"want this\"],\n  \"bitable_app_token\": \"PLACEHOLDER\",\n  \"bitable_table_id\": \"PLACEHOLDER\"\n}\n```\n\n## Execution\nThe skill is invoked by the parent agent with:\n```\nrun tts_hair_scout\n```\nThe parent agent must forward the LLM scoring request and the Feishu messaging/Bitable writes (the skill only returns the raw items and scores).\n\n---\n\n*When the skill is installed, a `index.ts` file in the same folder contains the runtime implementation.*\n","path":"~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/tts_hair_scout/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/auto","usage":{"input":35262,"output":993,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":36255,"cost":{"input":-35262,"output":-993,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":-36255}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774593083416,"responseId":"gen-1774593087-iG68vkxKUKobUYvhtIy2"}}
